Description: A high-angle, long shot features grainy, overexposed, and damaged film footage of a crowd of people, possibly in costume, with the clearest figure in the foreground being a dark, indistinct, almost triangular shape.
A grainy, high-contrast, low-light shot shows a crowd of people, partially obscured by a large, dark umbrella in the foreground.
A grainy, high-contrast, black and white shot shows a group of people, potentially on motorcycles, at night, with a shallow depth of field focusing on the face of a figure in the left mid-ground.
A grainy, high-contrast, low-key close-up shot in darkness reveals part of a figure's face, seemingly lit by a small, off-screen light source.
